OL,3,CMan charged with murder after man in
OL,4,Chis 90s found dead
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter the death of a man in his 90s at
OL,8,FRomney Marsh.
OL,10,FPolice and paramedics were called to a
OL,11,Freport of concern for a person in
OL,12,FHolly Road, St Mary's Bay at 9:20am on
OL,13,FThursday. (14 May)
OL,15,FA man was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,17,FA suspect was arrested and taken into
OL,18,Fcustody. It is understood that both
OL,19,Fmen were known to each other.
