OL,3,CMan charged with murder after man in
OL,4,Chis 90s found dead
OL,6,FThe following day, Mark Lambert, 66,
OL,7,Fwas charged with murder.
OL,9,FMr Lambert, of Cheriton Road,
OL,10,FFolkestone, was remanded in custody to
OL,11,Fappear before Folkestone Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt on Saturday. (16 May)
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
